n various activities. First, you can decorate it according to your preferences. You can also sleep to advance time, cook dishes that will restore your health and hunger, and change your clothes. Is your house very small? You can acquire one of the properties for sale in the village or in the city.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338200/extras/ad2349dd5a47dc03660d4430c80f0256.poster.avif?t=1726607855\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338200/extras/ad2349dd5a47dc03660d4430c80f0256.webm?t=1726607855\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2338200/extras/ad2349dd5a47dc03660d4430c80f0256.mp4?t=1726607855\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
